In the early exercises you worked on the following code 
var mailformat = /^\w+([\.-]?\w+)*@\w+([\.-]?\w+)*(\.\w{2,3})+$/
What is this?
Email validation
How does it work 
It check that there is an @ in your email
How is it implemented?
You compare it to what the user entered
